# Drop operator-supplied upstream RPMs (e.g. bastion-edge-*.rpm produced by
# `yarn release:rpm` in the bastion-edge source repo) here before running
# `make VARIANT=bastion-edge image`.
#
# Pin accepted sha256 in EXPECTED_SHA256 (sha256sum format, one line per RPM).
# `make repo` verifies each RPM against this manifest before createrepo and
# fails on mismatch.
